videos.headline: Perkins airs it out for long Virginia TD
videos.description: Virginia gets on the board first, as Bryce Perkins goes deep and connects with Joe Reed for a 40-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perkins airs it out for long Virginia TD) 2019/09/06

videos.headline: Virginia defense comes up with pick-6
videos.description: William & Mary QB Hollis Mathis has his pass picked off by Nick Grant who returns it back 85 yards to the house.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Virginia defense comes up with pick-6) 2019/09/06

videos.headline: Perkins keeps it himself for Virginia score
videos.description: Virginia takes a commanding 21-0 lead as QB Bryce Perkins scampers into the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perkins keeps it himself for Virginia score) 2019/09/06

videos.headline: Virginia's Chatman makes diving grab in end zone
videos.description: Virginia QB Bryce Perkins throws to Terrell Chatman who lays out in the end zone for a 15-yard touchdown.
